file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  title: "Customer Service"
  termsOfService: ""
  contact:
    name: "open knowledge GmbH"
    email: "info@openknowledge.de"
    url: "http://www.openknowledge.de"
  license:
    name: "Apache License, Version 2.0"
    url: "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0"
  version: "1"
  description: "A customer service"
paths:
  /api/customers/{id}:
    get:
      operationId: "getCustomer"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: "object"
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
            application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
              schema:
                type: "object"
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
          description: "default response"
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: "object"
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
            application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
              schema:
                type: "object"
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
          description: "default response"
      parameters:
      - style: "simple"
        required: true
        name: "id"
        in: "path"
        schema:
          nullable: true
          type: "integer"
    put:
      operationId: "updateCustomer"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
      parameters:
      - style: "simple"
        required: true
        name: "id"
        in: "path"
        schema:
          nullable: true
          type: "integer"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
            schema:
              type: "object"
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: "object"
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
        required: false
    delete:
      operationId: "deleteCustomer"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
      parameters:
      - style: "simple"
        required: true
        name: "id"
        in: "path"
        schema:
          nullable: true
          type: "integer"
  /api/customers:
    get:
      operationId: "getCustomers"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  type: "object"
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
                type: "array"
            application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
              schema:
                items:
                  type: "object"
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
                type: "array"
          description: "default response"
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  type: "object"
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
                type: "array"
            application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
              schema:
                items:
                  type: "object"
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
                type: "array"
          description: "default response"
      parameters: []
    post:
      operationId: "createCustomer"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                nullable: true
                properties: {}
                type: "object"
          description: "default response"
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/vnd.ok.customer.v1+json:
            schema:
              type: "object"
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: "object"
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
        required: false
components:
  schemas:
    Customer:
      properties:
        firstName:
          type: "string"
        lastName:
          type: "string"
        emailAddress:
          type: "string"
        gender:
          nullable: true
          type: "string"
          enum:
          - "FEMALE"
          - "MALE"
          - "UNSPECIFIED"
        name:
          type: "object"
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/CustomerName"
        id:
          nullable: true
          readOnly: true
          type: "integer"
      type: "object"
    CustomerName:
      properties:
        firstName:
          type: "string"
        lastName:
          type: "string"
      type: "object"
  requestBodies:
    Customer:
      content:
        '*/*':
          schema:
            type: "object"
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Customer"
      required: false
